    pkgdown template

    This is a template for a FTRPack GitHub repository, R package, and pkgdown website. It will have a NMFS palette, appropriate license and disclaimer, and a NMFS footer with logo. It has GitHub Actions that will automatically rebuild the site whenever the files are changed. The instructions will use the usethis and pkgdown packages. So install those.

    pkgdown uses Readme.md but to pull in the Disclaimer and footer from FIT, which migh change in the future, you need a Rmd file. When you update the Readme.Rmd file, you need to remember to knit the file to update Readme.md. You could make a GitHub Action to do this.
